    <h3>Professional Obligations</h3>
    <p>All work related to expert witness services is subject to professional ethical obligations and applicable rules of court.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>8. Contact Form and Communications</h2>

    <h3>Information Collection</h3>
    <p>Information submitted through the contact form is collected for the purpose of responding to your inquiry and evaluating potential expert witness engagements.</p>

    <h3>Communications</h3>
    <p>By submitting the contact form, you consent to communications from Dr. Lavian or TelecommNet regarding your inquiry.</p>

